comments.body:
@CooperLi I think this happens because we create a new file on the server end , since we transfer file from client and a new temporary file is created on server end on every request this causes final digest to change on every image commit. This behavior has been like this for a while, i traced back to version 3.0.0. Tagging @vrothberg for info.

Although the digest changes the content will be same cause under the hood its same tar file but with different metadata. 

Since the original concurrency issue is resolved i am closing this thread :) but please feel free to comment below if something is unresolved and we can re-open this.
